rComments: I took VPMA90 with Alexander Rapoport. Going into the course i thought it was going to be hard and he was going to be strict, but he took time and helped me during his office hours to make me understand, he provides valuable feedback, and cares about his students. He is highly respected by his students. He resemble s old man marley from home alone

He is passionate about his students and the subject matter, and is a great teacher. the course material is hard, but he will do everything he can to help you and genuinely wants you to understand. Wonderful person and amazing professor. Our class has the highest respect for him.

A very knowledgeable, funny, humble professor. He gives extra lessons and answers your questions until you are completely satisfied. He also tells good jokes and analogies to help you understand course material. I highly recommend taking his course.

Theory class A90...This guy is secretly as a teacher who actually wants you to learn how to do something..and do it well! The assignments are short but tough so get help...either from him or your friends. I always hated theory but it's not as bad when you got a prof like him. Got a good mark :D:D P.S. epic composer beard LOL
